寧次就係為咗佢個分家命運，但阿凱開完八門都唔撚洗死。<br />\n銀魂作為搞笑漫畫死咁多人已經算多<br />\n鬼滅個鬼殺隊任何一個人都係消耗品，同死神護廷十三隊好似，不過鬼殺隊有仇恨做驅動連班雜病都唔會淆，個個臨死都要爆seed換到對面血。<br />\n咒術好似都唔係死好多人姐，佢本身角色又唔算多。不過嗰個誘餌女仔咁死又真係估唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鏈鋸人咁嘅世界觀啲人都係死咗幸福啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac8cedce91a1c7c243ab01b1d79bdd20aa29e22","tid":2407291,"uid":213844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:56:57.000Z","msg":"而家興快節奏 二百幾話已經可以完 火影二百幾連疾風傳都未到"},{"pid":"21837025fd9bbd3f505305a3a6845c3809939531","tid":2407291,"uid":65770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e3117cd10b55c1573b8639393312a4ea3b210df","tid":2407291,"uid":166707,"like":32,"dislike":7,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T03:59:04.000Z","msg":"好似巨人既團長咁，要消費哂個角色既所有價值，咁先死得有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼滅算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:59:56.000Z","msg":"簡直係榨乾最後一滴血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9952856a9242644b6327d2ceb2570f3884b79b6","tid":2407291,"uid":241250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0e3117cd10b55c1573b8639393312a4ea3b210df","tid":2407291,"uid":166707,"like":32,"dislike":7,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T03:59:04.000Z","msg":"好似巨人既團長咁，要消費哂個角色既所有價值，咁先死得有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼滅算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T09:03:55.000Z","msg":"有得死已經算好 火影死左都要拎返出來繼續消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beef091c94efc11c32e1e3405db848cacaee6c0d","tid":2407291,"uid":5763,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T09:05:14.000Z","msg":"所以我都好唔鐘意妖尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><b